    'content1_2' => 'ADAM Bit provides you with a platform that matches your trades with open orders from other users of our services at your direction. Users are not able to predetermine a trade with a particular user or with a particular account. Additionally, an order may be partially filled or may be filled by multiple matching orders.',
    'content1_2_1' => 'Our Services',
